                <h2>ABOUT PAC</h2>
                <p class="about1">The Pet Adoption Center (PAC) is a compassionate organization dedicated to ending pet homelessness and finding loving families for abandoned animals.<br> <br>
                     Founded on the belief that every pet deserves a second chance, PAC works tirelessly to rescue, rehabilitate, and rehome cats, dogs, and other companion animals.
                </p>
