                <h2>OUR MISSION</h2>
                <p class="about1">PAC aims to:<br><br>
                    - Rescue pets from shelters, streets, and unsafe conditions.<br>
                    - Provide medical care, vaccinations, and spay/neuter services.<br>
                    - Match animals with responsible, caring adopters.<br>
                    - Educate communities about responsible pet ownership and animal welfare.<br>
                    </p>

            </div>
            <div class="section">
                <h2>WHY ADOPT FROM PAC?</h2>
                <p class="about1">By adopting from PAC, you’re not just getting a pet but you’re saving a life. Every adoption creates space for another animal in need, helping to reduce overcrowding in shelters.<br>
                    <br> PAC welcomes volunteers, fosters, and donors who want to make a difference. Join us in our mission to create a world where no pet is left without a home.

                    </p>

