                    <p><strong>Q: Is there an adoption fee?</strong><br>A: Yes, a small fee is required to cover veterinary costs and care.</p>
                    <p><strong>Q: Do you adopt animals?</strong><br>A: PAC does not adopt animals we rescue them.</p>
                    <p><strong>Q: Can I return my adopted pet if I change my mind?</strong><br>A: A pet is a lifetime commitment. However, if you truly can't keep your adopted pet, Please return them to us so we can find another home for them.</p>
